messages.text: Did you make it home safely??
I guess you could say that :P
Did you even see Katerina last night?
It was like she was doing it on purpose.
I’m sure she doesn’t know how you feel about him
Or maybe she does and she’s just being a jerk
Tiffany told me she does this all the time
well if Tiffany said it’s true…
rolling my eyes at you so hard lol
I’m gonna give her a taste of her own medicine
I’m gonna mess with her right back
how fun was that party last night??
you seemed like you had a really good time
I’m surprised I made it home in one piece
this is kind of weird for me to have to tell you but
I want you to hear it from me first
I really hope you didn’t hook up with Thomas last night
but someone told me that he’s got something
that you can’t get rid of
if you know what I mean
you didn’t hear it from me
I really hope you didn’t do anything with him
I think you should talk to him
I’m going to talk to him now!
LOL I told her he gave her an STD
I want to know what he’ll say
did you tell Thomas off yet?
I just came…to confront him about it…
He acted like he didn’t know what I was talking about
things got out of hand and…
I don’t think he’s breathing Kora!
I didn’t mean to push him that hard
Kora you have to help me
you have to help me do something about this
we have to move to the body or something
oh my god I can’t go to jail
you need to get over here now
you’re the one who told me I should confront him
I’m only here because of you
I have the text messages that prove it
you have to help me now
ok I’m going to my car now
oh my god I can’t believe this is happening
I just wanted to play a stupid joke oh my god
I was just messing with you
I didn’t think this would happen
Thomas is bleeding out on the floor
I know I know I know
oh my god I’m so sorry
I’m getting into my car now
I can’t believe you fell for that
for the same reason you lied about Thomas
just wanted to get you back
you knew I was lying the whole time?
I feel so stupid about this
if you liked Thomas you could have just said so
he’s not my boyfriend or anything
now you know what lies can do
anyway, I didn’t hook up with Thomas that night
wait, how’d you know I was lying?
